node.text: Imagine waking up and not having anything. Imagine everything you worked hard for and built turned to dust! I need everybody to understand that life isn’t promised. What happened to Haiti is horrific and I wouldn’t wish this on my worst enemy. Praying for everyone who has been affected by this earth quake and will continue to keep you in my prayers. -Love Coi

Sat down with uncle @snoopdogg and I swear he’s one of the greatest person I ever met. So real. So gangsta. Just a real ass person and I can’t wait until this interview come out 💫💫💫🔥🔥🔥🔥👑👑💓 thank you for the game fr. It’s stuck w me 4Lyfe
